This paper discusses power management in data centers, which is a topic related to distributed computing and computer architecture. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also involves simulation and analysis, which could fall under cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper discusses power consumption and quality-of-service, which could be relevant to cs.PF (Performance) and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
